Main screen:

- Search courses (brings up dialog) -> course listings
- Browse course categories -> Categories
- My courses
- Logged in as <name> / Not logged in  (no link)

Course listings
  - Course item list
    - Thumb
    - Title

Categories listing -> Category refinement (topics/software selection)

Category refinement
  - Show Topics -> Category - browse by topics
  - Show Software -> Category - browse by software

Category - Browse by topics
  - List of topics to do with category -> Course listings

Category - Browse by software
  - List of software to do with car -> Course listings
